WEBVTT

00:12:29.590 --> 00:12:34.227
and politics has come to resemble

00:12:34.227 --> 00:12:38.828
a sport that inspires more aggressiveness

00:12:38.828 --> 00:12:42.140
and pessimism than social cohesion

00:12:42.140 --> 00:12:46.413
and the desire for civic protaganism.

00:12:46.413 --> 00:12:48.439
Barack Obama won

00:12:48.439 --> 00:12:54.716
— (Applause) —

00:12:54.716 --> 00:12:58.279
because he mobilized people as never before

00:12:58.279 --> 00:13:00.812
through the use of social networks.